E3LDON.mac v5.5 by Kroaking
Updated for usage under E3 envioronment system.
Fully integrated / migrated away from standard MQ EQBCS commands to E3 /e3bca command structure.
All command systems for interacting with bots now supports E3BCS and MQ2DanNet.
Incorporated SwarmPull method for mob pulling, config file now supports SwarmPull option. If TRUE, camp 
locations are used for mass agro swarm pulls.
Version is specific to Project Lazarus server for Temple of Marr and PoK Magus teleport usage.

E3LDON.mac v6.0 by Kroaking
Incorporated RoundRobin and ThemeCheck camp selection methods:
RoundRobin .. cycles between all camps..  skipping last camp won. (ThemeCheck=FALSE)
ThemeCheck .. determines how many wins needed by camp/theme to max your augment stats/get COH, 
skips last camp won and then selects the camp you need the most wins in.
toon will pick camp with LEAST amount of LDON theme wins, and 
attempt to skip the last successful camp theme completed.

E3LDON.mac v6.1 contribution by Venoryk
Added exception sub to handle wait lock for file data being written which was causing steparray 
to go out of bounds on multiple array creation/deletion. Dungeon SpawnSteplocation array data should be 
created dynamically for each dungeon now.

E3LDON.mac v6.2 by Kroaking
Reworked ThemeSelect to properly detect camp theme completion and switch to Round Robin if done with LDON themes.
Cleaned up code for window state opens
---  Reworked the SpawnSteps for many of the dungeons to not pull deadly trains !!! 
---  ( a few more steps won't kill ya, but a few less WILL !)

E3LDON.mac v6.3 by Kroaking
Removed UseLogOut functionality and declares.
Revisited and updated Group End/Mana/Death check routines..   removed GroupHealth and its ini settings.

[Mana] MedAt=??  Should be set to what you currently have in your E3 INI file as: 
	[Misc] AutoMedBreak PctMana=30 ( if you have AutoMedBreak (On/Off)=On )

[Endurance] MedEndAt=?? Should be set to what you currently have in your E3 INI file as: 
	[Misc] AutoMedBreak PctMana=30 ( if you have AutoMedBreak (On/Off)=On )
	
Added BardSong INI section to define BardSong and BardSongSlot to play travel invis song.
	
This will be updated after Rekka pushes Exposed E3 ini settings to E3Bots to be captured via mono queries.

E3LDON.mac v6.4 by Kroaking
Incorporated many fixes from testing.
Cut over fully to E3 communication system, removal of UseE3BCS and UseDannet

E3LDON.mac v6.5 by Kroaking
Major improvements to the Looting system. 
Added AutoSellInPok option.

E3LDON.mac v7.0.0 by Kroaking
Complete revision of Single pull system to be in alignment with SwarmPull. 
Now uses Mob location to nav to.
OLD Combat system removed since E3 should handle all combat,
now in alignment with using DoClearTargets sub like SwarmPull does.
Cleaned up old code and INI call references for unused variables and procedures.

****************************************************************************************************************|
#event Magical_Presence "strange magical presence"
#event Sealed_Off "sealed off to you"
											   
#event Cannot_See "You cannot see your target"
#event Too_Far "Your target is too far away, get closer"
#event Cant_Hit "You can't hit them from here"

#event MissionFailed "#*#You failed to complete your adventure in time#*#"
#event MissionOver "#*#You have left your adventure#*#"
#event MissionSuccess "#*#You have sucessfully completed your adventure#*#"

#Event BagsFull "#*#There was no place to put that#*#"
#Event BagsFull "#*#There are no open slots for the held item in your inventory#*#"

#Event BackOffNow "#*#Try attacking someone other than yourself, it's more productive#*#"

#event NavMeshReload "#*#Could not locate destination on navmesh#*#"

#define /message "/echo \ay[\atE3LDoN\ay]\aw "

#bind AddToIgnore /ignorethese
#bind AddThisIgnore /ignorethis
#bind PermIgnore /permignore
#bind E3LDONCommand /E3LDoN

Sub Main
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub Main Entry
	
	/declare StuckSpamTimerSet	timer		outer	0
	/declare StuckSpamTrigger	timer		outer	0
	/declare OutX1 				int 		outer 	${Me.X}
	/declare OutY1 				int 		outer	${Me.Y}
	/declare OutZ1				int			outer	${Me.Z}
	/declare StuckCountOut 		int 		outer	0
	/declare BackUpTimer		int			outer 	0
	/declare GroupWaitTimer		int			outer	0
	/declare StuckSwitch		int 		outer
	/declare runcounter 		int 		outer	0
	/declare notkillable		int 		outer	0
	/declare Announce			bool		outer	FALSE
	/declare startTask 			int 		outer	${Zone.ID}
	/declare version			string		outer	7.1.5
	
	/message ==================================================================
 	/call Declares
	/message ==================================================================
	/message \at${MacroName}.mac \aw- \atv${version} \awby \ag Kroaking
	/message ==================================================================
	/delay 1s		
		
	/call CheckThings	

	|-------------------------------------
	|-- If No Adventure Time (no AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel) Check the starting zone, reset to Marrs if not in Pok or Marrs.
	/if ((${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}==0 && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}==0)) {
		/message \ayLooks like we do \arNOT\ax currently have a task assigned to us.
		/if (!${Select[${Zone.ID},202,386,22,30,34,35,68]} && ${NextCamp_Bark.Equal[NONE]}) {
			/message \ayLooks like we are \am[\atnot in a valid starting zone\am]\ay for LDoN zone routing.\ax
			/call GoToMarrs
			/call GoPoKMagus
		}
	}
	|-------------------------------------
	
	/if (${ForageTime}>0) /call CheckPlugin MQ2AutoForage
	/call CheckPlugin MQ2Melee
		
	/if (${Bool[${Plugin[MQ2Bucles]}]}) {
        /squelch /plugin MQ2Bucles unload noauto
        /message MQ2Bucles detected! This macro doesn't like it! Unloading temporarily ...
    }
	
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo \at/E3LDoN \ar***\at \agDebugging \arCode Tracing: \ayis set to \at[\ag${Debugging}}\at]
	
	/message ==================================================================
	/if (${HardMode}) {
		/message \ar***\at \agHardMode \arHigh Risk Task: \ayis set to \at[\ar${HardMode}\at] 
	} else {
		/message \ar***\at \agHardMode \arHigh Risk Task: \ayis set to \at[\ag${HardMode}\at] 
	}
	
	/if (${SwarmPull}) {
		/message \ar***\at \agSwarmPull \arHigh Risk PULLING: \ayis set to \at[\ar${SwarmPull}}\at] 
	} else {
		/message \ar***\at \agSwarmPull \arHigh Risk PULLING: \ayis set to \at[\ag${SwarmPull}}\at] 
	}
	/message ==================================================================

	/message \at/E3LDoN \awfor help \ayor \at/mqp \awto pause...
	/message \agGetting things ready, sit back...
	/delay 5s

	|-----------------------------------------------	
	/if (${Select[${Zone.ID},${GukTop},${Innothule},${AccursedSanctuary},${AncientAqua},${CauldronLostSouls},${ChapelOfTheWitnesses},${DrowningCrypt},${ForbodingPrison},${MushroomGrove},${RootGarden}]}) {
		/message ==================================================================
		/varset startTask ${SouthRo}
		/message \aySetting Start Task Zone \ay[\agSouthRo\ay]
		/message ==================================================================
	}
	/if (${Select[${Zone.ID},${GladiatorPits},${WindBridges},${BloodiedQuarries},${HallsOfWar},${HiddenVale},${DrudgeHollows},${Taskmasters},${BlazingForge},${ArenaOfChance},${BarracksOfWar}]}) {
		/message ==================================================================
		/varset startTask ${Commonlands}
		/message \aySetting Start Task Zone \ay[\agCommonlands\ay]
		/message ==================================================================
	}
	|-----------------------------------------------

	:mainloop
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${TempleofMarr} || ${Zone.ID} == ${PlaneofKnowledge}) /call GoPoKMagus
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub Main - MainLoop Entry
	
	|-----------------------------------------------
	/call GetAdventureStatus
	|------------------
	/message ==================================================================
	/call SetPetNoAlert
	/message ==================================================================
	|------------------
	|-----------------------------------------------	
	
	|---------------------------------------------------------------------------
	|-------------- ONLY DO LOGIC IF WE --HAVE-- AN ACTIVE ADVENTURE ASSIGNED !!!!!!
	|---------------------------------------------------------------------------
	/while (!${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_ProgressTextLabel].Text.Left[2].NotEqual[${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_ProgressTextLabel].Text.Right[2]}]} || ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
		/call GotoTask
		|----------------------------
		| ENGINE SELECT -- START
		|----------------------------
		/if (${SwarmPull})  {
			|----- CHECK MISSION SUCCESS IF WE JUST RESTARTED MACRO ------------
			/call CheckMissionSuccess
			|----- CHECK MISSION SUCCESS IF WE JUST RESTARTED MACRO ------------
			/message ==================================================================
			/message \aw<\ar*\ao*\ay*\ag*\at*\au*\am*\ap*\aw> \ayABOUT TO: - \arSWARM PULL\ay . . . get ready! \aw<\ap*\am*\au*\at*\ag*\ay*\ao*\ar*\aw> 
			/popcustom 13 5 ---> ABOUT TO SWARM PULL . . . get ready! <---
			/message ==================================================================
			/delay 5s
			|-----------------------------------
			|-- WHILE !(killcount=totalkillcount||No time left)
			|-----------------------------------
			/while (!${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_ProgressTextLabel].Text.Left[2].NotEqual[${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_ProgressTextLabel].Text.Right[2]}]} || ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {

				|-----------------------------------------------
				| Before we Swarm pull ...   Check if we should loot Corpses.
				/if (${LootCorpse} && !${Me.XTarget[1].ID}) /call CheckForCorpses
				|-----------------------------------------------
				|----------------------------
				| -- Call check mission zone.
				|----------------------------
				/call CheckInADungeon
				/if (${InADungeon}==1) /call DoSwarmPull
				/call GMCheck			
			}
			|-----------------------------------
			|-- WHILE !(killcount=totalkillcount||No time left)
			|-----------------------------------			
		} else {
			|----- CHECK MISSION SUCCESS IF WE JUST RESTARTED MACRO ------------
			/call CheckMissionSuccess
			|----- CHECK MISSION SUCCESS IF WE JUST RESTARTED MACRO ------------		
			/message ==================================================================
			/message \aw<\ar*\ao*\ay*\ag*\at*\au*\am*\ap*\aw> \ayABOUT TO: - \agSINGLE PULL\ay . . . get ready! \aw<\ap*\am*\au*\at*\ag*\ay*\ao*\ar*\aw> 
			/popcustom 15 5 ---> ABOUT TO SINGLE PULL . . . get ready! <---
			/message ==================================================================
			/delay 5s
			|-----------------------------------
			|-- WHILE !(killcount=totalkillcount||No time left)
			|-----------------------------------			
			/while (!${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_ProgressTextLabel].Text.Left[2].NotEqual[${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_ProgressTextLabel].Text.Right[2]}]} || ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {

				|-----------------------------------------------
				| Before we Single pull ...   Check if we should loot Corpses.
				/if (${LootCorpse} && !${Me.XTarget[1].ID}) /call CheckForCorpses
				|-----------------------------------------------
				|----------------------------
				| -- Call check mission zone.
				|----------------------------
				/call CheckInADungeon
				/if (${InADungeon}==1) /call DoSinglePull
				/call GMCheck
			}
			|-----------------------------------
			|-- WHILE !(killcount=totalkillcount||No time left)
			|-----------------------------------
		}
		|----------------------------
		| ENGINE SELECT -- END
		|----------------------------
	}
	|---------------------------------------------------------------------------
	|-------------- ONLY DO LOGIC IF WE HAVE AN ACTIVE ADVENTURE ASSIGNED !!!!!!
	|---------------------------------------------------------------------------
	/call GoPoKMagus
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub Main - MainLoop Exit
	/goto :mainloop
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub Main Exit
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: Declares
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub Declares
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub Declares Entry
	/declare FarmMob 			string 	outer 
	/declare PullRange 			int 	outer 
	/declare MacroName			string	outer	E3LDoN
	/declare Settings			string	outer	${MacroName}_${Me.CleanName}.ini
	/declare FirstRun			int		outer	0
	
	|--------------------------------------
	/if (!${Ini[${Settings}].Length}) /varset FirstRun 1
	|--------------------------------------
	
	/message \ay${Settings} is the INI being used.
	/declare MobIgnore			string 	outer E3LDoN_MobIgnored.ini
	/declare Targets 			string 	outer
	/declare myTargetID 		int 	outer 0
	/declare myTargetIDLoc 		string 	outer 0
	/declare reportTarget 		timer 	outer 5s
	/declare startZone 			int 	outer ${Zone.ID}
	/declare courseCorrection 	timer 	outer 1s
	/declare CampY 				int 	outer ${Me.Y}
	/declare CampX 				int 	outer ${Me.X}
	/declare CampZ 				int 	outer ${Me.Z}
	/declare DebugRepeatTimer 	timer	outer 1s
	/declare SitDelay 			timer 	outer 5s
	/declare Endmac 			bool	outer FALSE
	/declare BagsAreFull		bool 	outer FALSE
	/declare CampRadius 		int 	outer 2500
	/declare ZRadius 			int 	outer 500
	
	|** SPECIFIC of E3LDON.mac/SwarmPull & Theme type declares **|
	|----------------------------------------------------------
	/declare ZoneCount				int		outer 	0
	|----------------------------------------------------------
	|--- DO NOT CHANGE THESE !!! ----
	/declare Guk_Wins_Max			int		outer 	70
	/declare Miragul_Wins_Max		int 	outer 	68
	/declare Mistmoore_Wins_Max 	int 	outer 	76
	/declare Ruj_Wins_Max 			int 	outer 	74
	/declare Tak_Wins_Max 			int 	outer 	78	
	|--- DO NOT CHANGE THESE !!! ----
	|----------------------------------------------------------
	/declare CampThemeArray[5,5]	string	outer
	/declare NextCamp_Num			int		outer	NULL
	/declare NextCamp_Theme			string	outer	NULL
	/declare NextCamp_Wins			int		outer	0
	/declare NextCamp_WinsToGo		int		outer	0
	/declare InADungeon				int		outer	0
	/declare Adventure_Progress		string	outer	NULL
	/declare CurrentDC				int		outer	0
	/declare CurrentDCAC			int		outer	0
	/declare ZoneIdentityNum		int		outer	NULL
	|----------------------------------------------------------		
	|** SPECIFIC of E3LDON.mac/SwarmPull & Theme type declares **|
	
	|** Declare colors their escape code for read-ability **|
	/declare Black 			string outer \ab
	/declare Blue   		string outer \au
	/declare Brown      	string outer \a-o
	/declare Cyan   		string outer \at
	/declare Gray			string outer \a-w
	/declare Green			string outer \ag
	/declare Pink   		string outer \am
	/declare Orange   		string outer \ao
	/declare Purple   		string outer \ap
	/declare Red   			string outer \ar
	/declare Teal   		string outer \at
	/declare White   		string outer \aw
	/declare Yellow  		string outer \ay
	/declare DarkGreen 		string outer \a-g
	/declare DarkMarroon	string outer \a-m
	/declare DarkPurple		string outer \a-p
	/declare DarkRed		string outer \a-r
	/declare DarkCyan		string outer \a-t
	/declare DarkBlue		string outer \a-u
	/declare DarkYellow		string outer \a-y
	|** End color declarations **|
	
	|** E3LDON.mac/PullFarm.mac type declares INIThings **|
	
	|** SPECIFIC of E3LDON.mac/PullFarm.mac type declares **|
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General Debugging bool TRUE
	|** SPECIFIC of E3LDON.mac/PullFarm.mac type declares **|

	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General AssistMe bool TRUE
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General AutoSellInPok bool FALSE
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General DoBurns bool FALSE
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General DoInvis bool TRUE	
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General GroupNavToMe bool TRUE
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General HardMode bool FALSE
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General LootMethod string DCONLY
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General MinItemValue int 10
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General SwarmPull bool FALSE
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General UseMerc bool FALSE
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General UseMq2Melee bool FALSE
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} General CheckBots bool TRUE
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} General LootCorpse bool FALSE
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} General ThemeCheck bool TRUE
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} General UseClickBuffs bool FALSE
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} General UseClickDamage bool FALSE
	
	/declare BRDTravelSong string  outer "Selo's Song of Travel"
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} BardSong BRDMelodyName string base
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} BardSong BRDTravelSongSlot string 11
	
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} Endurance MedEndAt int 8
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} Endurance MedEndTill int 100
	
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} Mana BardMed bool TRUE
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} Mana MedAt int 30
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} Mana MedTill int 100
			
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} Alerts AFKGM bool TRUE
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} Alerts UseBeep bool TRUE
	
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} Theme LastCompleted_Num int 0
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} Theme LastCompleted_Theme string NONE
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} Theme LastCompleted_TimeStamp string NONE
		
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} Theme LastSwarmed_Dungeon string NONE
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} Theme LastSwarmed_Step string 1
	
	/call CheckIni ${Settings} Theme NextCamp_Bark string NONE
	
	| Time to Forage after mission ends 18000 tenths of a second max = (30 minutes)
	/call CheckINI ${Settings} General ForageTime int 0
	|** End of LDON.mac/PullFarm.mac type declares **|
	
	|** Start ZoneID as variable **|
	/declare TempleofMarr int outer 386
	/declare PlaneofKnowledge int outer 202
		
	|** Takish Zones **|
	/declare NorthRo int outer 34
	/declare AntPalace int outer 270
	/declare BalanceChamber int outer 261
	/declare FadeTemple int outer 241
	/declare SandfallCorridors int outer 256
	/declare ShiftingTower int outer 236
	/declare SunkenLibrary int outer 231
	/declare PrismaticCorridors int outer 274
	/declare RiverRecollection int outer 251
	/declare SweepingTides int outer 266
	/declare RoyalObservatory int outer 246								 
	|** End Takish Zones **|
	
	|** Rujarkian Zones **|
	/declare SouthRo int outer 35
	|/declare NorthRo int outer 34
	/declare Commonlands int outer 22
	/declare BloodiedQuarries int outer 230
	/declare HallsOfWar int outer 235
	/declare WindBridges int outer 240
	/declare GladiatorPits int outer 245
	/declare DrudgeHollows int outer 250
	/declare Taskmasters int outer 255
	/declare HiddenVale int outer 260
	/declare BlazingForge int outer 265
	/declare ArenaOfChance int outer 269
	/declare BarracksOfWar int outer 273
	|** End Rujarkian Zones **|
	
	|** Mistmoore Catacombs Zones **|
	/declare LesserFaydark int outer 57
	/declare GreaterFaydark int outer 54
	/declare Butcherblock int outer 68
	/declare ForlornCaverns int outer 233
	/declare DrearyGrotto int outer 238
	/declare InvokedStone int outer 243
	/declare EternalAffliction int outer 248
	/declare TheSepulcher int outer 253
	/declare SummoningGrounds int outer 258
	/declare TheCesspits int outer 263
	/declare AislesOfBlood int outer 268
	/declare SanguinaryRites int outer 272
	/declare InfernalSanctuary int outer 276
	|** End Mistmoore Catacombs Zones **|
	
	|** Miragul's Zones **|
	/declare Everfrost int outer 30
	/declare ForgottenWastes int outer 257
	/declare FrostedHalls int outer 252
	/declare GrandLibrary int outer 275
	/declare HeartMenagerie int outer 262
	/declare HushedBanquet int outer 247
	/declare MawMenagerie int outer 237
	/declare MorbidLaboratory int outer 267
	/declare SilentGallery int outer 232
	/declare SpiderDen int outer 242
	/declare TheaterHorrors int outer 271
	|** End Miragul's Zones **|
	
	|** Deepest Guk Zones **|
	/declare Innothule int outer 46
	|/declare SouthRo int outer 35
	/declare AccursedSanctuary int outer 264
	/declare AncientAqua int outer 239
	/declare CauldronLostSouls int outer 229
	/declare ChapelOfTheWitnesses int outer 254
	/declare DrowningCrypt int outer 234
	/declare ForbodingPrison int outer 249
	/declare MushroomGrove int outer 244
	/declare RootGarden int outer 259
	/declare GukTop int outer 65
	|** End Deepest Guk Zones **|
	
	|** End ZoneID as Variable **|

	|-------------------------------	
	/if (${FirstRun}) {
		/message Created INI file ${Settings} with default values.
		/message Please edit the file and restart ${MacroName}.
		/message Ending Macro
		/end
	} else {
		/message Config loaded from ${Settings}.
	}
	|-------------------------------	
	
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub Declares Exit
		
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: CheckThings
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub CheckThings
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub CheckThings Entry
	
	/call CheckPlugin MQ2Nav
	/call CheckMesh
	/call CheckPlugin MQ2Events
	|-----------------------------
	/if (${UseMq2Melee}) {
		/call CheckPlugin MQ2Melee
	} else {
		/if (${Bool[${Plugin[MQ2Melee]}]}) {
			/message \ay -- Unloading \am[\atMQ2Melee\am]\ay plugin.
			/squelch /plugin MQ2Melee unload noauto
		}
	}
	|-----------------------------	
	/call CheckPlugin MQ2MoveUtils
	
	/if (${LootCorpse}) {		
		/message ==================================================================
		/message \ay--- \atENABLING\ax \am${MacroName}\ax LOOTING, we will loot corpses.
		/if (${LootMethod.Equal[DCONLY]}) {
			/squelch /lootoff
			/message \ay--- \agLOOTING METHOD:\ax (\am${LootMethod}\ax) we will only loot [\atDiamond Coin\ay] and \arHIGH VALUE ITEMS.\ax
			|------------------------------------------------
		}  
		/if (${LootMethod.Equal[E3]}) {
			/squelch /looton
			/message \ay--- \agLOOTING METHOD:\ax (\am${LootMethod}\ax) we will only loot according to \amE3\ax settings.
			/message \ay    [ if configured in your \amE3\ax config files. \ag(Loot Settings.ini)\ax ]
		}
		/message ==================================================================
	} else {
		/squelch /lootoff
		/message ==================================================================
		/message \ar--- DISABLING ${MacroName} LOOTING, YOU WILL NOT LOOT CORPSES !
		/message ==================================================================
	}

	
	/if (${Endmac}) /end
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub CheckThings Exit
	
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: CheckInADungeon
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub CheckInADungeon
	/if ( (${Select[${Zone.ID},264,239,229,254,234,249,244,259]}) || (${Select[${Zone.ID},257,252,275,262,247,237,267,232,242,271]}) || (${Select[${Zone.ID},233,238,243,248,253,258,263,268,272,276]}) ||	(${Select[${Zone.ID},230,235,240,245,250,255,260,265,269,273]}) || (${Select[${Zone.ID},270,261,241,256,236,231,274,251,266,246]}) ) {
		/varset InADungeon 1
	} else {
		/varset InADungeon 0
	}
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: GoToMarrs
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub GoToMarrs
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub GoToMarrs Entry
	/call CloseAdventureWnd
	/message \arOoops..   your not in a valid starting zone for macro, Gating to Marr !
	
	|Start in Marrs	
	/delay 10
	/e3bca /nav stop
	/e3bca /playmelody stop
	/e3bca /keypress x 
	/delay 6
	/e3bcaa /stand
	/delay 5
	/e3bca /alt act 511
	/nav stop
	/if (${Select[${Me.Class.ShortName},BRD]}) /playmelody stop
	/keypress x 
	/delay 6
	/stand
	/delay 5
	/alt act 511
	/delay 20s

	|----------------------------
	/while (${Group.Member[1].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[2].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[3].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[4].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[5].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[6].OtherZone}) {
		/squelch /e3bca /nav stop
		/squelch /e3bca /playmelody stop		 	
		/squelch /e3bca /keypress x 
		/delay 6
		/squelch /e3bca /stand
		/delay 5
		/squelch /e3bca /alt act 511
		/nav stop
		/if (${Select[${Me.Class.ShortName},BRD]}) /playmelody stop
		/keypress x 
		/delay 6
		/stand
		/delay 5
		/alt act 511
		/delay 20s
	}
	|----------------------------	
	
	/while (${Zone.ID} != ${TempleofMarr}) {
		/delay 5s
	}
	/call GroupWait
	/delay 2s
	
/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub GoToMarrs Exit
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: GoPoKMagus
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub GoPoKMagus
/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub GoPoKMagus Entry
	/call CloseAdventureWnd
|------------------------------
/if (${Zone.ID} == ${TempleofMarr}) {
	/message \agGoing to PoK . . .
	/delay 3s	
	|----------------------------
	/while (${Group.Member[1].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[2].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[3].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[4].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[5].OtherZone} || ${Group.Member[6].OtherZone}) {
		/squelch /e3bca /nav stop
		/squelch /e3bca /playmelody stop		 	
		/squelch /e3bca /keypress x 
		/delay 6
		/squelch /e3bca /stand
		/delay 5
		/squelch /e3bca /alt act 511
		/nav stop
		/if (${Select[${Me.Class.ShortName},BRD]}) /playmelody stop
		/keypress x 
		/delay 6
		/stand
		/delay 5
		/alt act 511
		/delay 20s
	}
	|----------------------------
	/squelch /e3bcaa /tar Klonopin
	/delay 5
	/squelch /e3bcaa /nav target
	/delay 5
	/while (${Navigation.Active}) {
		/call SetLoc
		/call CheckStuck
		/delay 5
	}
	/call GroupWait
	/delay 2s

	:BarkPoK
	/if (${Target.CleanName.Equal[Klonopin]}) {
		/e3bark poknowledge	
	} else {
		/squelch /e3bcaa /tar Klonopin
		/delay 5
		/goto :BarkPoK
	}
	/delay 2s
	/while (${Zone.ID} == ${TempleofMarr}) {
		/delay 5s
	}
	/delay 20s
}
|------------------------------
|------------------------------
/if (${Zone.ID} == ${PlaneofKnowledge}) {
	
	|--------------------------------------
	|/echo \ayMoving to a common loc in PoK . . .	
	|--------------------------------------
	|/delay 3s
	|/squelch /e3bcaa /nav loc 189.76 48.62 -116.87
	|/delay 3s
	|/while (${Navigation.Active}) {
	|	/call SetLoc
	|	/call CheckStuck
	|	/delay 5
	|}
	|/call GroupWait
	|--------------------------------------
	
	|--------------------------------------
	/if (${AutoSellInPok}) /call AutoSell_Loot
	|--------------------------------------
	
	/message \ayFinding Magus . . .
	|/delay 3s
	/squelch /e3bcaa /tar Magus Alaria
	/delay 5
	/squelch /e3bcaa /nav target
	/delay 5
	/while (${Navigation.Active}) {
		/call SetLoc
		/call CheckStuck
		/delay 5
		}
	/call GroupWait
	/delay 2s
		|--------------------------------------------------------------
		|-- IF WE ARE CHECKING THEME CAMP WINS FOR CHARM ! 
		|.. Theme Win to go/Lockout Select it.. else FLAT Round Robin
		|--------------------------------------------------------------
		/if (${ThemeCheck}) {
			/call SelectAdventureZone_TC
		} else {
			/call SelectAdventureZone_RR
		}
		|--------------------------------
		/delay 2s
		
		|--------------------------------------------------------------
		| Forece reset of LastSwarmed_Step and LastSwarmed_Dungeon
		|--------------------------------------------------------------
		/call IniChange "Theme" "LastSwarmed_Dungeon" ${Zone.ShortName}
		/call IniChange "Theme" "LastSwarmed_Step" 1
		|--------------------------------------------------------------
		
		/message \ayHeaded to: \ar[\at${NextCamp_Bark}\ar]\ax
		|--------------------------
		:BarkMagus
		/if (${Target.CleanName.Equal[Magus Alaria]}) {
			/e3bark ${NextCamp_Bark}	
		} else {
			/squelch /e3bcaa /tar Magus Alaria
			/delay 5
			/goto :BarkMagus
		}
		|--------------------------
		/delay 5s
		/while (${Zone.ID} == ${PlaneofKnowledge}) {
			/delay 5s
			}
		/delay 10s
	}
|------------------------------	
/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub GoPoKMagus Exit
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: GetAdventureStatus		
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub GetAdventureStatus
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub GetAdventureStatus Entry
	
	/message \ayGetting adventure status...
	/if (!${Group.Leader.Name.Equal[${Me.Name}]}) {
		/e3bct ${Group.Leader.Name} /makeleader ${Me.Name}
		/delay 2s ${Group.Leader.Name.Equal[${Me.Name}]}
		/delay 1s
		/if (!${Group.Leader.Name.Equal[${Me.Name}]}) {
			/message ${Red}You are not the group leader. Please get leadership of the group and try again. Ending Macro!
			/end
		}
	}
	/call OpenAdventureWnd
	/delay 1s
	|-- DONT Have a task !!!
	/if (${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[you are not currently assigned]}) {
		/message ==================================================================
		/message \am*** You are not currently assigned a task ***
		/message ==================================================================
		/call CloseAdventureWnd
		/call GetTask
		|-- DONT Have a task !!!
	} else /if (!${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
		/message ==================================================================
		/message \am*** You are not currently assigned a task ***
		/message ==================================================================
		/call CloseAdventureWnd	
		/call GetTask
		|-- Have a task !!!
	} else /if (${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} || ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {				
		/message ==================================================================
		/message \am*** You currently have an assigned task ***
		/message ==================================================================
		/call CloseAdventureWnd
		/call GotoTask
	}
	
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub GetAdventureStatus Exit
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: SelectAdventureZone_RR
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub SelectAdventureZone_RR
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub SelectAdventureZone_RR Entry
    /message \ayGetting theme from \ay[\atROUND ROBIN\ay]\ag status...
	
	|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	|-- Data will NOT populate untill you have loaded the AdventureRequestWnd THEN AdventureStatsWnd windows to have client get data at least ONCE !
	|   This opens the AdventureStatsWnd window and populates it naturally from within the AdventureRequestWnd window.
	|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	/call OpenAdventureStatsWnd
	/delay 5
	/call CloseAdventureStatsWnd
	/delay 5
	|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	
	
	/message ==================================================================
 	/message \aoCamp Theme List:
	/message \ayCamp \at1\ay: Theme: \agDeepest Guk\ax
	/message \ayCamp \at2\ay: Theme: \agMiragul's Menagerie\ax
	/message \ayCamp \at3\ay: Theme: \agMistmoore Catacombs\ax
	/message \ayCamp \at4\ay: Theme: \agRujarkian Hills\ax
	/message \ayCamp \at5\ay: Theme: \agTakish-Hiz\ax
	/message ==================================================================
	
	|-----------------------------------
	|- Retrieve the last mission results
	|-----------------------------------
	/varset LastCompleted_Num ${Ini[${Settings},Theme,LastCompleted_Num]}
	|-----------------------------------
	
	|-----------------------------------
	|- Echo the last mission results
	|-----------------------------------
	/message \agLast Mission Succes: \ayCamp:\am(\ag${LastCompleted_Num}\am) \ayTheme:\am(\ag${LastCompleted_Theme}\am) \ayTime:\am(\ag${LastCompleted_TimeStamp}\am)	
	/message ==================================================================
		
	/varcalc ZoneCount ${LastCompleted_Num}+1
    /if (${ZoneCount}>=6) /varcalc ZoneCount 1
		
	/if (${ZoneCount}==5) {
		/varset NextCamp_Num ${ZoneCount}
		/varset NextCamp_Theme Takish-Hiz
		/varset NextCamp_Bark North Ro
	}
    /if (${ZoneCount}==4) {
		/varset NextCamp_Num ${ZoneCount}
		/varset NextCamp_Theme Rujarkian_Hills
		/varset NextCamp_Bark Commonlands
	}
    /if (${ZoneCount}==3) {
		/varset NextCamp_Num ${ZoneCount}
		/varset NextCamp_Theme Mistmoore_Catacombs
		/varset NextCamp_Bark Butcherblock
	}	
	/if (${ZoneCount}==2) {
		/varset NextCamp_Num ${ZoneCount}
		/varset NextCamp_Theme Miraguls_Menagerie
		/varset NextCamp_Bark Everfrost
	}
    /if (${ZoneCount}==1) {
		/varset NextCamp_Num ${ZoneCount}
		/varset NextCamp_Theme Deepest_Guk
		/varset NextCamp_Bark South Ro
	}
		
	/message \ag The next \amLDON\ag \ay[\atROUND ROBIN\ay]\ag set to \ayCamp:\am(\ag${NextCamp_Num}\am) \ayTheme:\am(\ag${NextCamp_Theme}\am) \ayZone: \am(\ag${NextCamp_Bark}\am)
	
	|-------------------------------------------------------------------------
	| Write NextCamp_Bark to INI !!!! so we can check and pick up if en route.
	|-------------------------------------------------------------------------
	/call IniChange "Theme" "NextCamp_Bark" "${NextCamp_Bark}"
	|------------------------------------------------------------------------
	|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo CampNum=(${NextCamp_Num}) | CampTheme=(${NextCamp_Theme}) | CampBark=(${NextCamp_Bark}) | CampWins=(${NextCamp_Wins}) | CampWinsToGo=(${NextCamp_WinsToGo})
	|/echo CampNum=(${NextCamp_Num}) | CampTheme=(${NextCamp_Theme}) | CampBark=(${NextCamp_Bark}) | CampWins=(${NextCamp_Wins}) | CampWinsToGo=(${NextCamp_WinsToGo})
	/message ==================================================================
	|-- Go to ccamp recreiter zone
    /message \agSelecting zone \ay[\am${NextCamp_Bark}\ay].
	| -- Write STEP 1 to the ini file since we want to set our initial first step for that zone.
	|------------------------------------------
	/call ForeceSpawnStepReset
	|------------------------------------------
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub SelectAdventureZone_RR Exit
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: SelectAdventureZone_TC  (TO DO: Round Robin based on win needs)  (ThemeCheck)
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub SelectAdventureZone_TC
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub SelectAdventureZone_TC Entry
	/message \ayGetting theme from \ay[\atTHEME CHECK\ay]\ag status...
	
	/declare x 								int local
	/declare y 								int local
	/declare MostWinsNeeded 	int local 0
	/declare TempCampWins 		int local 0
	/declare TempCampWinsToGo	int local 0

	|------------------------------------------------------
	| Camp 1 *** Guk_Wins_Max			int		outer 	70
	| Camp 2 *** Miragul_Wins_Max		int 	outer 	68
	| Camp 3 *** Mistmoore_Wins_Max 	int 	outer 	76
	| Camp 4 *** Ruj_Wins_Max 			int 	outer 	74
	| Camp 5 *** Tak_Wins_Max 			int 	outer 	78	
	|------------------------------------------------------
		
	|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	|-- Data will NOT populate untill you have loaded the AdventureRequestWnd THEN AdventureStatsWnd windows to have client get data at least ONCE !
	|   This opens the AdventureStatsWnd window and populates it naturally from within the AdventureRequestWnd window.
	|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	/call OpenAdventureStatsWnd
	/delay 5
	/call CloseAdventureStatsWnd
	/delay 5
	|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	
	|-------------------------
	/declare Guk_Wins 			int	local ${Window[AdventureStatsWnd].Child[AdvStats_ThemeList].List[1,3]}
	/declare Miragul_Wins		int	local ${Window[AdventureStatsWnd].Child[AdvStats_ThemeList].List[2,3]}
	/declare Mistmoore_Wins		int	local ${Window[AdventureStatsWnd].Child[AdvStats_ThemeList].List[3,3]}
	/declare Ruj_Wins	 		int	local ${Window[AdventureStatsWnd].Child[AdvStats_ThemeList].List[4,3]}
	/declare Tak_Wins	 		int	local ${Window[AdventureStatsWnd].Child[AdvStats_ThemeList].List[5,3]}
	|-------------------------
	
	|------------------------------------------------------
	| HARD CODE FOR TESTING
	|------------------------------------------------------
	|/varset Guk_Wins		71 	
	|/varset Miragul_Wins	68
	|/varset Mistmoore_Wins	76
	|/varset Ruj_Wins		74
	|/varset Tak_Wins		78
	|------------------------------------------------------		

	|-------------------------
	/declare Guk_WinsToGo 		int	local ${Math.Calc[${Guk_Wins_Max} - ${Guk_Wins}]}
	/declare Miragul_WinsToGo 	int	local ${Math.Calc[${Miragul_Wins_Max} - ${Miragul_Wins}]}
	/declare Mistmoore_WinsToGo	int	local ${Math.Calc[${Mistmoore_Wins_Max} - ${Mistmoore_Wins}]}
	/declare Ruj_WinsToGo 	 	int	local ${Math.Calc[${Ruj_Wins_Max} - ${Ruj_Wins}]}
	/declare Tak_WinsToGo 	 	int	local ${Math.Calc[${Tak_Wins_Max} - ${Tak_Wins}]}
	|-------------------------	

	|------------------------------------------------
	|CampNum CampTheme CampBark CampWins CampWinsToGo
	|------------------------------------------------
	|---------------------	
	/varset CampThemeArray[1,1] 1
	/varset CampThemeArray[1,2] Deepest_Guk
	/varset CampThemeArray[1,3] South Ro
	/varset CampThemeArray[1,4] ${Guk_Wins}
	/varset CampThemeArray[1,5] ${Guk_WinsToGo}
	
	/varset CampThemeArray[2,1] 2
	/varset CampThemeArray[2,2] Miraguls_Menagerie
	/varset CampThemeArray[2,3] Everfrost
	/varset CampThemeArray[2,4] ${Miragul_Wins}
	/varset CampThemeArray[2,5] ${Miragul_WinsToGo}
	
	/varset CampThemeArray[3,1] 3
	/varset CampThemeArray[3,2] Mistmoore_Catacombs
	/varset CampThemeArray[3,3] Butcherblock
	/varset CampThemeArray[3,4] ${Mistmoore_Wins}
	/varset CampThemeArray[3,5] ${Mistmoore_WinsToGo}
	
	/varset CampThemeArray[4,1] 4
	/varset CampThemeArray[4,2] Rujarkian_Hills
	/varset CampThemeArray[4,3] Commonlands
	/varset CampThemeArray[4,4] ${Ruj_Wins}
	/varset CampThemeArray[4,5] ${Ruj_WinsToGo}
	
	/varset CampThemeArray[5,1] 5
	/varset CampThemeArray[5,2] Takish-Hiz
	/varset CampThemeArray[5,3] North Ro
	/varset CampThemeArray[5,4] ${Tak_Wins}
	/varset CampThemeArray[5,5] ${Tak_WinsToGo}
	|---------------------
	
	/message ==================================================================
 	/message \aoCurrent Theme Win Stats:
	/if (${Guk_WinsToGo}>0) {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[1,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[1,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Guk_Wins}\ay/\am${Guk_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\at${Guk_WinsToGo} Remaining\ay)
	}  else {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[1,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[1,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Guk_Wins}\ay/\am${Guk_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\arCOMPLETED\ay)
	}
	
	/if (${Miragul_WinsToGo}>0) {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[2,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[2,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Miragul_Wins}\ay/\am${Miragul_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\at${Miragul_WinsToGo} Remaining\ay)
	}  else {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[2,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[2,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Miragul_Wins}\ay/\am${Miragul_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\arCOMPLETED\ay)
	}
	
	/if (${Mistmoore_WinsToGo}>0) {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[3,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[3,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Mistmoore_Wins}\ay/\am${Mistmoore_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\at${Mistmoore_WinsToGo} Remaining\ay)
	}  else {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[3,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[3,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Mistmoore_Wins}\ay/\am${Mistmoore_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\arCOMPLETED\ay)
	}	
	
	/if (${Ruj_WinsToGo}>0) {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[4,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[4,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Ruj_Wins}\ay/\am${Ruj_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\at${Ruj_WinsToGo} Remaining\ay)
	}  else {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[4,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[4,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Ruj_Wins}\ay/\am${Ruj_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\arCOMPLETED\ay)
	}	
	
	/if (${Tak_WinsToGo}>0) {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[5,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[5,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Tak_Wins}\ay/\am${Tak_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\at${Tak_WinsToGo} Remaining\ay)
	}  else {
		/message \ayCamp ${CampThemeArray[5,1]}: \ag${CampThemeArray[5,2]}\ay: \ag(\am${Tak_Wins}\ay/\am${Tak_Wins_Max}\ay) --- (\arCOMPLETED\ay)
	}
	/message ==================================================================
		
	|-----------------------------------
	|- Retrieve the last mission results
	|-----------------------------------
	/varset LastCompleted_Num ${Ini[${Settings},Theme,LastCompleted_Num]}
	|-----------------------------------
	
	|-----------------------------------
	|- Echo the last mission results
	|-----------------------------------
	/message \agLast Mission Succes: \ayCamp:\am(\ag${LastCompleted_Num}\am) \ayTheme:\am(\ag${LastCompleted_Theme}\am) \ayTime:\am(\ag${LastCompleted_TimeStamp}\am)	
	/message ==================================================================
		
	|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	|/echo Starting: MostWinsNeeded=(${MostWinsNeeded})
	|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    /for x 1 to ${CampThemeArray.Size}
			/varset TempCampWins ${CampThemeArray[${x},4]}
			/varset TempCampWinsToGo ${CampThemeArray[${x},5]}
			|--------------
			|if (${TempCampWinsToGo}>0) /echo Processing Entry:(${x}) - TempCampWins:(${TempCampWins}) TempCampWinsToGo:(${TempCampWinsToGo})
			|--------------
        |-- if CampThemeArray[x] is greater than the currently set greatest number, AND we have WinsToGo |-- AND ~EXCLUDE THE CAMP NUM FROM SETTINGS WRITTEN AT LAST WIN
       /if (((${TempCampWinsToGo}>${MostWinsNeeded}) && (${TempCampWinsToGo}>0) && (${x}!=${LastCompleted_Num}))) {
			|--------------
			|/echo Processing Entry:(${x}) - Wins:(${TempCampWins}) Remaining:(${TempCampWinsToGo})
			|--------------
            |set the lowest number to myArray[x]
            /varset MostWinsNeeded ${CampThemeArray[${x},5]}
			/varset NextCamp_Num ${CampThemeArray[${x},1]}
			/varset NextCamp_Theme ${CampThemeArray[${x},2]}
			/varset NextCamp_Bark ${CampThemeArray[${x},3]}
			/varset NextCamp_Wins ${TempCampWins}
			/varset NextCamp_WinsToGo ${TempCampWinsToGo}
        }
		|/echo MostWinsNeeded-X is index # (${MostWinsNeeded}) --		
    /next x
	|-----
	|--------------------------------------------------------		
	/if (${MostWinsNeeded}>0) {
		/message \ag The next \amLDON\ag \ay[\atTHEME CHECK\ay]\ag set to \ayCamp:\am(\ag${NextCamp_Num}\am) \ayTheme:\am(\ag${NextCamp_Theme}\am) \ayZone: \am(\ag${NextCamp_Bark}\am)
		|-------------------------------------------------------------------------
		| Write NextCamp_Bark to INI !!!! so we can check and pick up if en route.
		|-------------------------------------------------------------------------
		/call IniChange "Theme" "NextCamp_Bark" "${NextCamp_Bark}"
		|------------------------------------------------------------------------
		|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		|/echo Ending: MostWinsNeeded=(${MostWinsNeeded})
		|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		/if (${Debugging}) /echo CampNum=(${NextCamp_Num}) | CampTheme=(${NextCamp_Theme}) | CampBark=(${NextCamp_Bark}) | CampWins=(${NextCamp_Wins}) | CampWinsToGo=(${NextCamp_WinsToGo})
		|/echo CampNum=(${NextCamp_Num}) | CampTheme=(${NextCamp_Theme}) | CampBark=(${NextCamp_Bark}) | CampWins=(${NextCamp_Wins}) | CampWinsToGo=(${NextCamp_WinsToGo})
		/message ==================================================================
		|-- Go to ccamp recreiter zone
		/message \agSelecting zone \ay[\am${NextCamp_Bark}\ay].
		| -- Write STEP 1 to the ini file since we want to set our initial first step for that zone.
		|------------------------------------------
		/call ForeceSpawnStepReset
		|------------------------------------------
	} else {
		/message ==================================================================
		/message \arYou have completed all LDoN themes, setting system to \ay[\atROUND ROBIN\ay]\ar in the INI and exiting.\ax
		/message ==================================================================
		/call IniChange "General" "ThemeCheck" FALSE
		/delay 20
		/end
	}
	|--------------------------------------------------------
	
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub SelectAdventureZone_TC Exit
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: GetTask
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub GetTask
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub GetTask Entry
	
	|----------- TEMPLE OF Marr / PLANE OF KNOWLEDGE ------------
	 /if (${Zone.ID} == ${TempleofMarr} || ${Zone.ID} == ${PlaneofKnowledge}) /call GoPoKMagus
	|----------- TEMPLE OF Marr / PLANE OF KNOWLEDGE ------------
	
	|----------- NORTH RO ------------
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${NorthRo}) {
		:getTaskNRo
		|-- /squelch /e3bcaa /removelev
		|/call CheckInvis
		/if (!${Defined[Recruiter]}) {
			/declare Recruiter string local Escon Quickbow
			/declare RecruiterLoc string local ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Y} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].X} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Z}
		}
		
		/if (${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Distance3D} < 20) {
			/call FindTask
		} else {
			/if (!${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
			/message \agGoing to \ay[\ap${Recruiter}\ay] \ag to pick up a task...	 
			/squelch /e3bcaa /nav loc 2699.06 931.71 -23.92			
			/call GroupWait			
			/delay 5
			/while (${Navigation.Active}) {
				/call SetLoc
				/call CheckStuck
				/delay 5
				}
			/squelch /e3bcaa /nav loc ${RecruiterLoc}
			/call GroupWait
			/delay 3s   
			/goto :getTaskNRo
			}
		}
		|- Move to avoid getting trapped in a tent  onroute to task.
		|---------------------------------------------
		/message \aoAvoiding tent obtacles at \at[\agNro Camp\at]
		/if (${runcounter}==0) /squelch /e3bca /nav loc 2661.87 976.10 -20.15
		/delay 5s
		/call NavToLoc2 2661.87 976.10 -20.15
		/call GroupWait
		/if (${Me.XTarget[1].ID}) /call DoClearTargets
		|---------------------------------------------		
		/delay 5
	}
	|----------- NORTH RO ------------
	
	|----------- COMMONLANDS ------------   && ${Zone.ID}==${startTask}
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${Commonlands}) {
		:getTaskCommon
		|-- /squelch /e3bcaa /removelev
		|/call CheckInvis
		/if (!${Defined[Recruiter]}) {
			/declare Recruiter string local Periac Windfell
			/declare RecruiterLoc string local ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Y} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].X} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Z}
		}
		/varset startTask ${Zone.ID}
		/message \aySetting Start Task Zone \ay[\ag${Zone.ID}\ay]
		/if (${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Distance3D} < 20) {
			/call FindTask
		} else {
			/if (!${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
			/message \agGoing to \ay[\ap${Recruiter}\ay] \ag to pick up a task...	
			/squelch /e3bcaa /nav loc ${RecruiterLoc}
			/call GroupWait
			/delay 3s   
			/goto :getTaskCommon
			}
		}
	}
	|----------- COMMONLANDS ------------ 
	
	|----------- BUTCHERBLOCK ------------
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${Butcherblock}) {
		:getTaskButcher
		|-- /squelch /e3bcaa /removelev
		|/call CheckInvis
		/if (!${Defined[Recruiter]}) {
			/declare Recruiter string local Xyzelauna Tu`Valzir
			/declare RecruiterLoc string local ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Y} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].X} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Z}
		}
		
		/if (${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Distance3D} < 20) {
			/call FindTask
		} else {
			/if (!${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
			/message \agGoing to \ay[\ap${Recruiter}\ay] \ag to pick up a task...	  
			/squelch /e3bcaa /nav loc ${RecruiterLoc}
			/call GroupWait
			/delay 3s   
			/goto :getTaskButcher
			}
		}
	}
	|----------- BUTCHERBLOCK ------------	
	
	|----------- EVERFROST ------------
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${Everfrost}) {
		:getTaskEFP
		|-- /squelch /e3bcaa /removelev
		|/call CheckInvis
		/if (!${Defined[Recruiter]}) {
			/declare Recruiter string local Mannis McGuyett
			/declare RecruiterLoc string local ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Y} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].X} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Z}
		}
		
		/if (${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Distance3D} < 20) {
			/call FindTask
		} else {
			/if (!${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
			/message \agGoing to \ay[\ap${Recruiter}\ay] \ag to pick up a task...	  
			/squelch /e3bcaa /nav loc ${RecruiterLoc}
			/call GroupWait			
			/delay 3s   
			/goto :getTaskEFP
			}
		}	
	}
	|----------- EVERFROST ------------	
	
	|----------- SOUTH RO ------------  && ${Zone.ID}==${startTask}
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${SouthRo}) { 
		:getTaskSRo
		|-- /squelch /e3bcaa /removelev
		|/call CheckInvis
		/if (!${Defined[Recruiter]}) {
			/declare Recruiter string local Kallei Ribblok
			/declare RecruiterLoc string local ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Y} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].X} ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Z}
		}
		/varset startTask ${Zone.ID}
		/message \aySetting Start Task Zone \ay[\ag${Zone.ID}\ay] 
		/if (${Spawn[${Recruiter}].Distance3D} < 20) {
			/call FindTask
		} else {
			/if (!${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
			/message \agGoing to \ay[\ap${Recruiter}\ay] \ag to pick up a task...	  
			/squelch /e3bcaa /nav loc ${RecruiterLoc}
			/call GroupWait
			/delay 3s   
			/goto :getTaskSRo
			}
		}
	}
	|----------- SOUTH RO ------------	
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub GetTask Exit
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: FindTask (Called from GetTask when at camp)
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub FindTask
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub FindTask Entry
	
	/declare LockoutLoopWait	int local	60
	
	/message \agGettting a Task . . .
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${NorthRo}) {
		/declare Recruiter string local Escon Quickbow
	}
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${Commonlands}) {
		/declare Recruiter string local Periac Windfell
	}
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${Butcherblock}) {
		/declare Recruiter string local Xyzelauna Tu`Valzir
	}
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${Everfrost}) {
		/declare Recruiter string local Mannis McGuyett
	}
	/if (${Zone.ID} == ${SouthRo}) {
		/declare Recruiter string local Kallei Ribblok
	}
	:ReGetTaskFromLockout
	/delay 4s
	/if (${Target.ID} != ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].ID}) /target id ${Spawn[${Recruiter}].ID}
	/delay 2s ${Target.ID}==${Spawn[${Recruiter}].ID}
	/invoke ${Target.RightClick}
	/delay 1s ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Open}
	/notify AdventureRequestWnd AdvRqst_RiskCombobox listselect ${If[${HardMode},2,1]}
	/delay 1s
	|set Type to Mob Count
	/notify AdventureRequestWnd AdvRqst_TypeCombobox listselect 3
	/delay 1s
	/notify AdventureRequestWnd AdvRqst_RequestButton leftmouseup
	/delay 3s
	/delay 1s ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[Slay]}
	/delay 1s ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_AcceptButton].Enabled}
	/notify AdventureRequestWnd AdvRqst_AcceptButton leftmouseup
	/delay 1s
	/squelch /target clear
	
	/if (${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
		/message ==================================================================
		/message \ay${If[${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[Slay]},This appears to be a slay count task \atHardMode \ayis set to \at[\ag${HardMode}\at],]}
		/message \ay${If[${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[Kill]},This appears to be a kill count task \atHardMode \ayis set to \at[\ag${HardMode}\at],]}
		/message \ay${If[${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[Ridding]},This appears to be a ridding count task \atHardMode \ayis set to \at[\ag${HardMode}\at],]}		
		/message ==================================================================
		|----------------------------------------------------------
		| -- Write STEP 1 to the ini file since we want to set our initial first step for that zone.
		|------------------------------------------
		|/echo SUB FIND TASK
		/call ForeceSpawnStepReset
		|------------------------------------------		
	} else {
		/message ==================================================================
		/message  \ay${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text}
		/message  \ay${If[${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[The Number of adventures returned was zero]},You appear to be in lockout mode for this camp \at[\arWAITING\at]\ay for \at(\ag${LockoutLoopWait}\at)\ay seconds to try again.,]}
		/message ==================================================================
		/delay ${LockoutLoopWait}s
		/goto :ReGetTaskFromLockout
	}
	
	/call CloseAdventureWnd
	
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub FindTask Exit
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: AcceptTask
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub AcceptTask
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub AcceptTask Entry
	/delay 5s ${Window[TaskSelectWnd].Open}
	/notify TaskSelectWnd TSEL_AcceptButton leftmouseup
	/delay 5s !${Window[TaskSelectWnd].Open}
	/delay 5
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub AcceptTaskExit
/return
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| SUB: GotoTask
| --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Sub GotoTask
	/if (${Debugging}) /echo Sub GotoTask Entry
	
	/message \agGoing to Task . . .
	/if (${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[try adding more players]}) {
		/message \arThere are no tasks available to you. \atDo you have the right levels? 
		/message \ayDo you have enough members in your group?
		/end
	}

|----------- BUTCHERBLOCK ------------
/if (${Zone.ID} == ${Butcherblock} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} || ${Zone.ID} == ${Butcherblock} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
		/message ${Zone.ID} vs Butcherblock: ${Butcherblock}
		:getoutalive3
		/call GroupWait
		/if (${DoInvis}) /call CheckInvis
		
		/if (${runcounter}==0) /squelch /e3bca /nav loc -1318.19 -3086.02 3.12
		/delay 1s
		/call NavToLoc2 -1314.01 -3058.35 5.90
		/delay 5
		/while (${Navigation.Active}) {
			/call SetLoc
			/call CheckStuck
			/delay 20
		}
		/call GroupWait
		/if (${Me.XTarget[1].ID}) /call DoClearTargets
		/if (${runcounter}==0) {
			/squelch /e3bca /face heading 260
			/delay 2s
			/squelch /e3bca /keypress forward hold
			/delay 3s
			/squelch /e3bca /keypress forward
			/delay 1s
		} 
		/squelch /face heading 260
		/delay 2s
		/squelch /keypress forward hold
		/delay 3s
		/squelch /keypress forward
		/delay 1s
		/call Zoning
		/if (!${Zone.ID} == ${Butcherblock} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[you are not currently assigned]}) /goto :getoutalive3
		/varcalc ZoneCount 4
}
|----------- BUTCHERBLOCK ------------	
	
|----------- GREATER FAYDARK ------------
/if (${Zone.ID} == ${GreaterFaydark}) {
		/message ${Zone.ID} vs Butcherblock: ${Butcherblock}
		/call GroupWait
		/if (${DoInvis}) /call CheckInvis
		
		|----------------------
		/if (${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[unearthed grave]} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} || ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[unearthed grave]} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} || ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[Find a crypt]} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} || ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[Find a crypt]} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {	
			/if (${runcounter}==0) /squelch /e3bca /nav loc -2624.00 -1113.00 3.12			
			/delay 1s
			/call NavToLoc2 -2610.80 -1113.13 3.12
			/delay 5
			/while (${Navigation.Active}) {
				/call SetLoc
				/call CheckStuck
				/delay 20
			}
			/call GroupWait
			/if (${Me.XTarget[1].ID}) /call DoClearTargets
			/squelch /e3bca /face heading 175
			/delay 2s
			/squelch /e3bca /keypress forward hold
			/delay 3s
			/squelch /e3bca /keypress forward
			/delay 1s
			/squelch /face heading 175
			/delay 2s
			/squelch /keypress forward hold
			/delay 3s
			/squelch /keypress forward
			/delay 1s
			/call Zoning
		}
		|-------------------
}
|----------- GREATER FAYDARK ------------
	
|----------- LESSER FAYDARK ------------
/if (${Zone.ID} == ${LesserFaydark} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} || ${Zone.ID} == ${LesserFaydark} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
	    /message ${Zone.ID} vs Butcherblock: ${Butcherblock}
		/call GroupWait
		/if (${DoInvis}) /call CheckInvis
		
		|----------------------
		/if (${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[unearthed grave]} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} || ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[unearthed grave]} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
			/message \aoHeaded to an \at[\agunearthed grave\at]
			/if (${runcounter}==0) /squelch /e3bca /nav loc -111.31 3861.35 -39.73
			/delay 1s
			/call NavToLoc2 -111.31 3861.35 -39.73
			/delay 5
			/while (${Navigation.Active}) {
				/call SetLoc
				/call CheckStuck
				/delay 20
			}
			/call GroupWait
			/if (${Me.XTarget[1].ID}) /call DoClearTargets
			
			/message \agEveryone is here. \ayGoing in to task...
			/doevents
			/squelch /e3bca /removelev
			/squelch /e3bca /dropinvis
			/squelch /e3bca /doortarget MISTPORT701
			/delay 2s
			/squelch /e3bca /click left door
			/squelch /removelev
			/squelch /dropinvis
			/squelch /doortarget MISTPORT701
			/delay 2s
			/squelch /click left door
			|-----------------------
			/call Zoning
			/call GenerateList
			/call ForeceSpawnStepReset
			/call ResetBard
			/delay 2s
			/squelch /e3bcg /multiline ; /afollow off ; /nav stop ; /stand
			/delay 5
			/squelch /followoff
			|-----------------------			
		}
		|----------------------
		
		|----------------------
		/if (${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[Find a crypt]} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} || ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_NPCText].Text.Find[Find a crypt]} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
			/message \aoHeaded to a \at[\agcrypt\at]
			/if (${runcounter}==0) /squelch /e3bca /nav loc -755.00 3831.00 1.84
			/delay 1s
			/call NavToLoc2 -755.00 3831.00 1.84
			/delay 5
			/while (${Navigation.Active}) {
				/call SetLoc
				/call CheckStuck
				/delay 20
			}
			/call GroupWait
			/if (${Me.XTarget[1].ID}) /call DoClearTargets
			
			/message \agEveryone is here. \ayGoing in to task...
			/doevents
			/squelch /e3bca /removelev
			/squelch /e3bca /dropinvis
			/squelch /e3bca /doortarget MISTFCFN700
			/delay 2s
			/squelch /e3bca /click left door
			/squelch /removelev
			/squelch /dropinvis
			/squelch /doortarget MISTFCFN700
			/delay 2s
			/squelch /click left door
			|-----------------------
			/call Zoning
			/call GenerateList		
			/call ForeceSpawnStepReset
			/call ResetBard
			/delay 2s
			/squelch /e3bcg /multiline ; /afollow off ; /nav stop ; /stand
			/delay 5
			/squelch /followoff
			|-----------------------
		}
		|----------------------
}		
|----------- LESSER FAYDARK ------------		
	
|----------- EVERFROST ------------
/if (${Zone.ID} == ${Everfrost} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} || ${Zone.ID} == ${Everfrost} && !${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_EnterTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length} && ${Window[AdventureRequestWnd].Child[AdvRqst_CompleteTimeLeftLabel].Text.Length}) {
		/message ${Zone.ID} vs Everfrost: ${Everfrost}				
		:getoutalive61
		/call GroupWait
		/if (${DoInvis}) /call CheckInvis
		
		|-----------------
		|SHIMMERING PORTAL
		|-----------------
